title: DDFP 391: Week 4 preview & 'If quarterbacks were vegetables'
itunes:title: DDFP 391: Week 4 preview & 'If quarterbacks were vegetables'
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank (in London!!!) and Elliot Harrison to make their Week 4 picks during the "Red Challenge Flag Picks" segment. Shek also checks in with Ike Taylor live from Pittsburgh ahead of the Steelers' Thursday night matchup against the Ravens. Plus, in his farewell show, Sully behind the glass introduces a new segment where quarterbacks are compared to … vegetables? Check it out!
